{"tid":1026401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈譴責香港警察出動四十警力，處理獨派人士一人集會","createTime":"2019-02-18T05:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T10:27:57.000Z","uid":2429,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3394392a870e706bd76e2cca81f5fcb9652694","tid":1026401,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2048175568795148/posts/2279928078953228/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2048175568795148%2Fposts%2F2279928078953228%2F&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=39aadcce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2048175568795148/posts/2279928078953228/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警察 Hong Kong Police出動四十警力，處理獨派人士一人集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcPHJLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcPHJLt.jpg&h=5db3b139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2048175568795148/posts/2280117422267627/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2048175568795148%2Fposts%2F2280117422267627%2F&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=2420af16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2048175568795148/posts/2280117422267627/</a><br />\n<br />\n【公民教育堂】<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，有鑑於香港警察公安化情況嚴重，如果大家真係咁唔好彩好似今日關同學咁比警察無理查牌呢，你可以要求警員交代其合理犯罪懷疑嘅，因為<br />\n<br />\n根據警察條例(第232章)第54條(1)，警務人員要在「發現任何人行動可疑」下，才可「截停該人以要求他出示身分證明文件」；及第54條(2)，警務人員「發現任何人是他合理地懷疑已經或即將或意圖犯任何罪行者」，才可「截停該人以要求他出示身分證明文件」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4X3hxD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4X3hxD6.jpg&h=18afc57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐關sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7713498637fde098267408f85cdf3ccb0a13ec8","tid":1026401,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"十死士都冇<br />\n宜家得返一個<